title: OnePlus 9RT receives new OxygenOS update with bug fixes and stability improvements
content:
After releasing the first post-launch OxygenOS update to the OnePlus 9RT last month, OnePlus is now rolling out another update for its latest affordable flagship. Interestingly, unlike the OxygenOS builds that rolled out to other OnePlus 9 series and OnePlus Nord devices over the last few weeks, the new OxygenOS update for the OnePlus 9RT

description: OnePlus has started rolling out a fresh OxygenOS update for the OnePlus 9RT with bug fixes and stability improvements. Download from the links in the post.
